    "description": "<strong>《马拉维拉岛的奇禽异兽》</strong> 是一款3D冒险游戏，你将化身年轻的野生动物摄影师，走进马拉维拉岛神奇的生态系统，邂逅各种非同寻常的生物，了解生物的习性，通过摄影记录它们的魅力与风采——这才是最重要的一步。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378020/extras/e95454ae406f0b9ed17a698e8c7ffef7.poster.avif?t=1729016645\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378020/extras/e95454ae406f0b9ed17a698e8c7ffef7.webm?t=1729016645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378020/extras/e95454ae406f0b9ed17a698e8c7ffef7.mp4?t=1729016645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>马拉维拉岛的魔法结界日渐薄弱，只有人类再次相信世间存在魔幻之物，海岛的结界才不会消失。化身初出茅庐的野生动物摄影师玛丽娜·蒙特斯，带上爷爷的日记和相机，踏上马拉维拉岛，跋山涉水，解开谜题，发现各种动物与植物，通过相机捕捉奇禽异兽的风采。<br><br>你要与它们耐心、友好地互动，才能了解其独特的习性！与桀骜不驯的獭鳄嬉戏，帮助坠入爱河的禽猴求爱，寻找香蕉鸟最爱的藏身之地。走进《马拉维拉岛的奇禽异兽》的世界，随时都能以特别而友好的方式与岛上的生物互动！<br><br>捕捉你与这些生物的美妙瞬间，向世界展示马拉维拉岛的神奇！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378020/extras/befc55ecac39295aea2f2594cdb25b78.avif?t=1729016645\" width=600 height=105 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378020/extras/80c15d0514abe7e2dafca3fe8f55a487.poster.avif?t=1729016645\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378020/extras/80c15d0514abe7e2dafca3fe8f55a487.webm?t=1729016645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378020/extras/80c15d0514abe7e2dafca3fe8f55a487.mp4?t=1729016645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>大大小小50多种特别的生物可以互动、拍照<br></li><li>三个生态区域各不相同，每个区域均有特别的物种，等你来探索！<br></li><li>生态环境壮丽秀美，无限美景等你记录<br></li><li>谜题重重，需要与生物互动、配合才能解开</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378020/extras/cd690d829c026203edcf44ef71399f31.poster.avif?t=1729016645\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378020/extras/cd690d829c026203edcf44ef71399f31.webm?t=1729016645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1378020/extras/cd690d829c026203edcf44ef71399f31.mp4?t=1729016645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
